{"id":"808016508878012416","type":"text","timestamp":1770584591,"post_url":"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/goodtransgirl/808016508878012416","is_reblog":true,"added_content":false,"tags":[],"reblog_ready":false,"body":"<p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://sharkgirldick.tumblr.com/post/718957505402847232/complete-i-guess-ill-be-cumming\">sharkgirldick</a>:</p><blockquote><p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://sharkgirldick.tumblr.com/post/718957001975169024/hey-warrior-you-didnt-think-you-could-just\">sharkgirldick</a>:</p><blockquote><p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://sharkgirldick.tumblr.com/post/718956728598790144/psst-hey-you-want-the-real-source-of-the\">sharkgirldick</a>:</p><blockquote><p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://sharkgirldick.tumblr.com/post/718953370793181184/what-those-brutish-dwarves-would-have-you\">sharkgirldick</a>:</p><blockquote><p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://sharkgirldick.tumblr.com/post/718943495726989312/kill-yourself-no-no-noble-warrior-i-said-kill\">sharkgirldick</a>:</p><blockquote><p>Kill yourself? No no, noble warrior. I said &ldquo;kill those elves!&rdquo; Those bastards have had it coming for far too long. Here, take this axe. </p><p><span class=\"npf_color_rachel\"><b>AXE OF FROST</b></span><b> added to your inventory.</b></p><p>Good luck out there.</p><p><span class=\"npf_color_joey\"><b>QUEST STARTED</b></span><b>: I Guess They Have It Coming</b></","trail":[{"blog":{"name":"sharkgirldick"},"post":{"id":"718943495726989312"}},{"blog":{"name":"sharkgirldick"},"post":{"id":"718953370793181184"}},{"blog":{"name":"sharkgirldick"},"post":{"id":"718956728598790144"}},{"blog":{"name":"sharkgirldick"},"post":{"id":"718957001975169024"}},{"blog":{"name":"sharkgirldick"},"post":{"id":"718957505402847232"}}],"baseline_notes":4985,"baseline_ts":1774705101.464}